(249, 2, '2010-11-08 14:37:10', '2010-11-08 14:37:10', '<p>I loaded the table with materials collected from the landscape and they responded in different ways: making sculpture, drawing, taking photographs, involving the scale model figures.</p>\r\n<p><a rel="attachment wp-att-250" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/group1/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-250" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/group1-640x426.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a rel="attachment wp-att-251" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/landscape1/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-251" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/landscape1-320x480.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="480" /><a rel="attachment wp-att-257" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/drawing/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-257" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/drawing-640x426.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a></a></p>\r\n<p><a rel="attachment wp-att-251" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/landscape1/"></a><a rel="attachment wp-att-252" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/landscape-2/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-252" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/landscape-2-640x426.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a rel="attachment wp-att-255" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/drawing-with-mud/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-255" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/drawing-with-mud-320x480.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="480" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a rel="attachment wp-att-253" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/landscape3/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-253" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.