1/landscape3-640x426.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-254" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/landscape4/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-254" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/landscape4-640x426.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-256" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/sculpture-at-coldwell-centre/structure-for-landscape/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-256" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2010/11/structure-for-landscape-640x426.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a>\r\n\r\nsuch a lot came through this session: building structures , manipulating scale with the materials &amp; the model figures, exploring narrative, drawing with twigs, exploring textures, manipulating materials, borrowing ideas from each other.', 'sculpture at Coldwell Centre', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '249-revision-3', '', '', '2010-11-08 14:37:10', '2010-11-08 14:37:10', '', 249, 'http://watershed.sallybarker.local/249-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
