hment wp-att-486" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/cartwright-hall-private-view/9-susanna-text/"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-486" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2011/07/9-susanna-text-640x471.jpg" alt="" width="318" height="234" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><a rel="attachment wp-att-485" href="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/cartwright-hall-private-view/9a-lombardis-susanna/"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-485" src="http://watershed.sallybarker.local/files/2011/07/9a-Lombardis-susanna-360x480.jpg" alt="" width="316" height="422" /></a></p>', 'Cartwright Hall private view', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '464-revision-19', '', '', '2011-07-12 09:54:15', '2011-07-12 09:54:15', '', 464, 'http://watershed.sallybarker.local/464-revision-19/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
