(114, 3, '2012-09-20 15:56:14', '2012-09-20 14:56:14', 'I like to use strange and forgotten or overlooked spaces to show work in. They often translate in something very positive, powerful and meaningful. \r\n\r\nThey present the un-beautiful, imperfect but interesting and characterful. Giving attention to something previously missed lets us look closer at our environment and sometimes invest in the community.\r\n\r\nI have a lot of experience exhibiting my own and a wide range of other peoples work in very diverse venues.', 'Display in neglected spaces', 'I like to use strange and forgotten or overlooked spaces to show work in. They often translate in something very positive, powerful and meaningful. ', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'display-in-neglected-spaces', '', '', '2012-12-01 22:56:56', '2012-12-01 21:56:56', '', 0, 'http://sallybarker.local/?page_id=114', 4, 'education', '', 0),
