(587, 1, '2012-09-25 01:57:14', '2012-09-25 00:57:14', 'These comics tell the ongoing story of Deirdre, a struggling artist, and her encounters with the intergalactic superhero Teela and the megalomaniacal gallerist Miffy Tweeb. They present a surreal and mystifying picture of an art world populated by aliens, celebrities, and misfits, all seemingly oblivious to the fate of the main character whose imagination and thoughts are exposed in the texts. The most recent four of the comic strips were drawn in response to requests from everything magazine by Steve Rushton and Luci Eyers. Without their support, some of these comics may never have been realised.', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '587', '', '', '2012-10-16 23:40:22', '2012-10-16 22:40:22', '', 0, 'http://sallybarker.local/?p=587', 8, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
